                    {% embed '_partials/faq/item.twig' with {'title': 'How do I change my Steam profile to public?'} %}
                        {% block content %}
                            Our system automatically checks if you meet our ETS2 and/or ATS requirements.
                            In order for us to do this, we need your Steam profile to be set to public.
                            <br><br>
                            If you're unsure on how to do this, you can follow <a
