                                rel="noopener noreferrer">these</a> instructions.
                            <br><br>
                            Please make sure that "Game details" is set to
                            <b>public</b>, and that the "Always keep my total playtime private even if users can see my game details." checkbox is
                            <b>unchecked</b>.
                        {% endblock %}
                    {% endembed %}

                    {% embed '_partials/faq/item.twig' with {'title': 'How do I change my TruckersMP ban history to public?'} %}
