                            <br><br>
                            You can do this <a href="https://truckersmp.com/profile/settings" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a>.
                            <br><br>
                            Please make sure that the "Display your bans on your profile and API" checkbox is
                            <b>checked</b>.
